---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy & Terms | Pondering Silver"
  description="Learn how Pondering Silver approaches privacy, data storage, and the in-progress nature of the site."
>
  <article class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-10 text-gray-700">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy &amp; Terms of Service</h1>
      <p>
        Transparency matters. This site is actively evolving, and everything here is offered in that spirit of ongoing craftsmanship and discovery.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Development Status</h2>
      <p>
        This website is currently in development. All features and functionalities are provided “as is” and should be used at your own risk. We make no warranties about the completeness, reliability, or accuracy of this website.
      </p>
      <p>
        As this site is hosted on Netlify&apos;s free tier, it may become temporarily unavailable if monthly usage limits are exceeded.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Data Storage &amp; Privacy</h2>
      <p>We prioritize your privacy and maintain complete transparency about data handling:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
        <li>All data is stored exclusively on your device (client-side storage).</li>
        <li>Deleting your browser&apos;s local storage will delete all saved data.</li>
        <li>We do not track, collect, or retain any personal information.</li>
        <li>No data is transmitted to or stored on our servers—because they don&apos;t exist.</li>
        <li>Your information remains private and under your control at all times.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>By using this website, you acknowledge and agree that:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
        <li>The website is provided “as is” without any warranties.</li>
        <li>You use the website and its features at your own risk.</li>
        <li>We are not liable for any data loss or consequences that result from using this website.</li>
        <li>Features and functionality may change as development continues.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
